<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hinna Thiengtho Siempa.</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hinna thiengtho siempa a deih puou Zion ah,
 Minsiet leh lungkhamna puo chun a matsak ui;
 A changthak nete kha dogal a suok zo tau,
 A nung a hun zui ui mipi simsenloh hawn,
 Juda'n ma a pui a thepthaka matsak guo'n

[V2]
 2. Tichun a man taua , Thiempu Lal insung ah,
 Thimthu a tiemsak ui Linglukhuk khu dingin;
 Linglukhuk a ngau ie Lalpa luchung achun,
 Khut in a zuk beng un, thisan va zung zungin,
 Ka Hukdampa pui ui, Kalvari lam zuonin.

[V3]
 3. Thing ana sutuoh ui. Kalvari tang chunga,
 Kilhna a sekkhawl ui, Ka Lalpa kilhna ding ;
 Ka Lal a khai kang ui A mel muol thipthiep in,
 A nak ah a sun ui thisan leh tui a pawt,
 Zion kulhpi sungah gal vai a hawm khiel ui.

[V4]
 4. A gensau mah bangin Hukdampan a thuok tai,
 A tiemsau mah bangin Hukdampa a thi tai;
 Van mithiengthote khun lingpi ling zungzung in,
 Lautha a kaitho ui, sietlei a zal sate
 Hukdampa puldo di'n khawthieng ah a leng ui.

[V5]
 5. Na thawkna ngilh tiengleh gitlohna a zing sek,
 Mit chu a hun tuom ui, Na vak hawih lieh dingin;
 Tuhin hun hawkthan la, Na eng vak singseng in,
 Na mela hehpihna mittui vazung zungin,
 Ka lunggil gilo ah Lalpa hung leng inla.</lyrics>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>46</hymn_number>
</song>